  <brief_title>Esophageal Manometry and Impedance Study in Obese Patients Before and During Anesthesia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Esophageal Pressures and Reflux in Obese Patients Before and During Anesthesia Using High-resolution Solid-state Manometry</official_title>
